data.description:
- 3500 English Words: Elementary, Pre-intermediate, Intermediate and Upper Intermediate;
- it is possible to add the words and the translation to them in any languages (1*);
- the personal teacher with display of words in the set time (2*);
- app is using built-in notifications and doesn’t occupy free slots (3*);
- app works without the Internet (4*).

All words have been translated into 79 languages: Afrikaans, Albanian, Arabic, Armenian, Azerbaijani, Basque, Belarusian, Bengali, Bosnian, Bulgarian, Catalan, Cebuano, Chinese, Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch, Esperanto, Estonian, Filipino, Finnish, French, Galician, Georgian, German, Greek, Gujarati, Haitian Creole, Hausa, Hebrew, Hindi, Hmong, Hungarian, Icelandic, Igbo, Indonesian, Irish, Italian, Japanese, Javanese, Kannada, Khmer, Korean, Lao, Latin, Latvian, Lithuanian, Macedonian, Malay, Maltese, Maori, Marathi, Mongolian, Nepali, Norwegian, Persian, Polish, Portuguese, Punjabi, Romanian, Russian, Serbian, Slovak, Slovenian, Somali, Spanish, Swahili, Swedish, Tamil, Telugu, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Urdu, Vietnamese, Welsh, Yiddish, Yoruba, Zulu

1* Можно добавлять свои слова и перевод к ним на любых языках.
2* Личный учитель с показом слов в указанное время.
3* Приложение использует встроенные уведомления, что позволяет не занимать свободные слоты.
4* Приложение работает без Интернета.
